body:
Enable [no-else-return](https://eslint.org/docs/latest/rules/no-else-return) eslint rule

it removes `else` statements that can be removed

e.g. 

```
if (a) {
  return true;
} else {
  return false;
}
```

becomes

```
if (a) {
  return true;
}

return false;
```

which is an equivalent
